<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="past-n">past <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /pɑːst/    美 /pæst/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-the-past">1.★ <strong>[the past] 过去；[语法] 过去式：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Writing letters seems to be a thing of <strong>the past</strong>. 
写信好像是过去的事情了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>In the past</strong>, appearing on television wasn’t for ordinary people. 
在过去，普通人上不了电视。</p><footer>2008 上海</footer></div>

<h4 id="2-c">2.★ <strong>[C] [单数] (过去的) 经历：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a country with a glorious past
有着光辉历史的国家</p></div></div>